featured_reviews.review_id:
Eidgah is specific place of offering community Namaz in special festivals.
People go there on Eid-Ul-Fitr and Eid-Ul-Zuha. Both festivals brings happiness in our lives. Eidgah is decorated for offering Namaz and on those days(I mentioned above) people offer namaz together. Then they wish each other . And then Sewaiyan( special dish).
We really love going to friends home, eating Sewaiyan and having fun.
Eidgah is sorrounded with thelas of chaat , fuchka, ice cream , chawmin, Manchurian ,etc. And huge hustle is seen for buying these tasty fast foods.
